<dt id="1_05">
What if I don’t think I can get a lucrative career?
</dt>

<dd>
<p>High Impact Careers isn’t exclusive to future millionaires.  No matter what your career prospects are, our arguments are relevant to you.</p>

<p>If you decide to pursue one of the most high impact career that are available to you, then we warmly welcome you into the High Impact community.</p>
